## 🔧 Configuration

### Cursor Settings (.qwen/config.json)
```json
{
  "cursor_adapters": {
    "enabled": true,
    "auto_detect": true,
    "pipeline_integration": true
  },
  "agent_mapping": {
    "research": ["ANALYST", "ARCHITECT", "PLANNER", "DESIGNER"],
    "code": ["DEVELOPER", "QA_TESTER", "CODE_REVIEWER"]
  }
}
```

### Agent Command Templates

**Research Agent Template:**
```
🎯 Research Mode
📋 Policy: AI_POLICY.md
📄 Focus: {file_type}
🚀 Action: {analysis_type}
```

**Code Agent Template:**
```
💻 Code Mode
📋 Policy: AI_POLICY.md
📄 Focus: {file_type}
🚀 Action: {operation_type}
⚠️  Protocol: {debug_protocol}
```

